针对 VoicePepper 这类 macOS 桌面应用，以下是可行的端到端测试方案：

---

## macOS Swift 应用端到端测试方案

### 方案一：XCUITest（官方标准方案）

在 Xcode 中添加 UI Testing Target，通过 Accessibility 层自动化操控 UI：

```swift
// VoicePepperUITests.swift
import XCTest

class VoicePepperUITests: XCTestCase {
    let app = XCUIApplication()

    override func setUpWithError() throws {
        continueAfterFailure = false
        app.launch()
    }

    // 验证状态栏图标存在
    func testStatusBarIconExists() {
        // 需要 accessibilityIdentifier 标记 UI 元素
        let menuBarExtra = app.statusItems["VoicePepper"]
        XCTAssertTrue(menuBarExtra.exists)
    }

    // 验证点击图标展开 Popover
    func testPopoverOpensOnClick() {
        let statusItem = app.statusItems["VoicePepper"]
        statusItem.click()

        let popover = app.popovers.firstMatch
        XCTAssertTrue(popover.waitForExistence(timeout: 2))
    }
}
```

**关键**：给 SwiftUI 元素加 `accessibilityIdentifier`：

```swift
// TranscriptionListView.swift
ScrollView { ... }
    .accessibilityIdentifier("transcriptionList")
```

---

### 方案二：Swift Snapshot Testing（推荐配合 Claude Code）

这是让 Claude Code 能"看见"SwiftUI 界面的核心技巧（来自 [twocentstudios.com](https://twocentstudios.com/2025/07/13/giving-claude-code-eyes-to-see-your-swiftui-views/) 的实践）：

```bash
# 添加依赖
# .package(url: "https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-snapshot-testing", from: "1.17.0")
```

```swift
import SnapshotTesting
import SwiftUI

class TranscriptionPopoverTests: XCTestCase {
    func testPopoverEmptyState() {
        let state = AppState()
        let view = TranscriptionPopoverView().environmentObject(state)
        assertSnapshot(of: NSHostingController(rootView: view), as: .image)
    }

    func testPopoverWithEntries() {
        let state = AppState()
        state.entries = [TranscriptionEntry(text: "测试转录文本", timestamp: Date(), duration: 1.5)]
        let view = TranscriptionPopoverView().environmentObject(state)
        assertSnapshot(of: NSHostingController(rootView: view), as: .image)
    }
}
```

快照图片会保存到 `__Snapshots__/` 目录，Claude Code 可以直接读取图片文件做视觉验证。

---

### 方案三：Xcode 26.3 + Claude Agent SDK（最新）

根据 Anthropic 公告，Xcode 26.3 内置了 Claude Agent SDK，支持：
- Claude 直接捕获 **Xcode Previews** 截图并迭代修改
- 通过 **MCP** 协议让 Claude Code CLI 连接 Xcode 获取预览图
- 形成「改代码 → 截图 → 分析 → 再改」的自动闭环

---

### 方案四：单元测试（最快验证逻辑）

对 VoicePepper 的核心服务进行单元测试，覆盖 7.1-7.6 的场景：

```swift
class VADDetectorTests: XCTestCase {
    func testSegmentFiredAfterSilence() {
        let vad = VADDetector()
        var receivedSegment: [Float]?
        vad.onSegmentComplete = { receivedSegment = $0 }

        // 模拟 500ms 语音 + 600ms 静音
        let speech = [Float](repeating: 0.1, count: 8000)  // 500ms @ 16kHz
        let silence = [Float](repeating: 0.0, count: 9600) // 600ms
        vad.feed(samples: speech)
        vad.feed(samples: silence)

        XCTAssertNotNil(receivedSegment)
        XCTAssertEqual(receivedSegment?.count, speech.count + silence.count)
    }

    func testForceFlushAt30Seconds() {
        let vad = VADDetector()
        var flushed = false
        vad.onSegmentComplete = { _ in flushed = true }

        // 连续 30s 语音（无停顿）
        let longSpeech = [Float](repeating: 0.5, count: 16000 * 30 + 1)
        vad.feed(samples: longSpeech)

        XCTAssertTrue(flushed)  // 应在 30s 处强制 flush
    }
}

class AudioRingBufferTests: XCTestCase {
    func testOverflowProtection() {
        let buffer = AudioRingBuffer(capacitySamples: 100)
        var overflowed = false
        buffer.overflowPublisher.sink { overflowed = true }.store(in: &cancellables)

        buffer.write([Float](repeating: 0, count: 150))  // 超过容量
        XCTAssertTrue(overflowed)
        XCTAssertEqual(buffer.sampleCount, 100)
    }
}
```

---

### 在 Claude Code 中的推荐工作流

**对 VoicePepper 最实用的组合：**

| 测试类型 | 工具 | 覆盖场景 |
|------|------|------|
| 核心逻辑 | XCTest 单元测试 | VAD、环形缓冲区、模型管理 |
| SwiftUI 视图 | Snapshot Testing | Popover、状态栏各状态外观 |
| 完整链路 | XCUITest | 快捷键→录音→转录→UI 显示 |

Claude Code 无法像浏览器应用那样直接操控原生 macOS App（没有 Playwright 等价物），但通过 **快照图片** 可以让 Claude Code 看到界面状态。

Sources:
- [Giving Claude Code Eyes to See Your SwiftUI Views](https://twocentstudios.com/2025/07/13/giving-claude-code-eyes-to-see-your-swiftui-views/)
- [Apple XCTest Documentation](https://developer.apple.com/documentation/xctest)
- [Swift Testing – Apple Developer](https://developer.apple.com/xcode/swift-testing/)
- [I Shipped a macOS App Built Entirely by Claude Code](https://www.indragie.com/blog/i-shipped-a-macos-app-built-entirely-by-claude-code)
- [Apple's Xcode now supports the Claude Agent SDK](https://www.anthropic.com/news/apple-xcode-claude-agent-sdk)

